name: SuperDAO.us
description:
The SuperDAO.us community is raising funds for its “Super Bowl Art Exhibition Spot” in collaboration with BPNFT.co, targeted to air during the 2023 Super Bowl.
Currently, funds will be used to send a lucky Contributing Artist to the SuperBowl on February 13th, 2022, and fund the community and its other projects throughout the year.

SuperDAO.us is a collaborative community of artists, collectors and advocates established to help fellow artists “break-out,” gain exposure, thrive, and support themselves and others in our new Web3 “Creator Economy” world.
payDisclosure: This is not meant as a security or investment.
